  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>Decorated in flame motifs and intricate filigree, this deep-sided brass container holds burning coals. When a fire is lit in the brazier and the proper summoning words are spoken (1 full round), a Large fire elemental appears under the command of the speaker, functioning as a summon monster VI spell. If brimstone or alchemist's fire is added, the elemental is Huge instead of large, and the brazier works as a summon monster VII spell. Only one elemental can be summoned at a time. A new elemental requires a new fire, which cannot be lit until after the first elemental disappears (or is dispelled, dismissed, or slain).<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Wondrous Item, summon monster VII</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Rappan Athuk",
